sequenceDiagram
    actor Customer
    participant UI as Browser UI
    participant View as Booking View
    participant Form as BookingForm
    participant Car as Car Model
    participant Booking as Booking Model
    participant DB as MySQL Database

    Customer->>UI: Select car and open booking page
    UI->>View: GET booking page
    View->>Car: Fetch selected car
    Car->>DB: Read car data
    DB-->>Car: Car record
    Car-->>View: Car object
    View-->>UI: Render booking form

    Customer->>UI: Submit booking details
    UI->>View: POST booking data
    View->>Form: Validate input
    Form->>DB: Check overlapping bookings
    DB-->>Form: Validation result

    alt Invalid dates or overlap exists
        Form-->>View: Error
        View-->>UI: Show validation message
    else Valid booking
        Form-->>View: Cleaned data
        View->>Booking: Create booking
        Booking->>Booking: Calculate days and cost
        Booking->>DB: Save booking
        DB-->>Booking: Booking saved
        View->>Car: Update availability
        Car->>DB: Set is_available false
        DB-->>Car: Car updated
        View-->>UI: Show booking confirmation
    end
